  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">START Funds  Diarrhoea  Outbreak Bulawayo</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1) Provision of potable water to 9 public institutions = individuals
2) Hygiene education and awareness (A) face-to-face sessions and B) mass media SMS &amp; radio campaign)
2) Hygiene kit distribution to 1200 vulnerable households (soap, chlorine tab, jeri-cans)
4) Handwashing Facilities at public places</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Success will be that the outbreak is brought under control and there are no deaths or new incidences of the disease. People are able to focus on their lives and livelihoods in the midst of the Covid-19 situation.</narrative>
  </description>
